  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Shampoo\" target=\"_blank\">Shampoo</a><br />\n\tShampoo is a cleaning <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/agent\" target=\"_blank\">agent</a> for the hair. Who is using the shampoo? What ingredients are in the shampoo? What is the color of the shampoo? How about the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/texture\" target=\"_blank\">texture</a> and smell?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They poured the shampoo into their hands... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) staff washing a client's hair in a beauty <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/salon\" target=\"_blank\">salon</a><br />\n\t2) chemists working on a new formula for a new line of shampoo with exotic ingredients<br />\n\t3) received a free sample of a shampoo from a promotional event<br />\n\t4) home-made shampoo with organic ingredients, environmentally friendly without <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/harsh\" target=\"_blank\">harsh</a> chemicals<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe warm water ran down his face as he ran his fingers through his hair, the last of the shampoo and soap bubbles washed down the drain. It was very relaxing to stand under warm running water after a stressful day at work. He wiped the water off his face. It felt great to be able to use both arms with ease. Several days ago, he went to the hospital for a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/checkup\" target=\"_blank\">checkup</a> on his previously injured arm. At that point, the stitches were already taken out. There was no infection and the wound healed well, the scar barely noticeable.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161956643541/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721257/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721257\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p596036/\">TED演讲：如何在6个月内学会任何一种外语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724208/\">一饱眼福！这10个国家总是产美女！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p628819/\">为什么睡过头反而更疲倦?</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723989/\">太震惊！现实中也有“灰姑娘”</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p704005/\">美元为何叫1刀 货币名称起源大盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724091/\">新东方名师邱政政:四步打造地道美音II</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723668/\">2015两会 李克强答记者问双语全文</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2p