  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/podcasts/artwork/266/witness.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722337\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tIt's almost 40 years since the forces of the Khmer Rouge stormed into the capital of Cambodia, Phnom Penh. It was the start of a four-year <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/reign\" target=\"_blank\">reign</a> of terror in which up to 2 million people are thought to have died. Mike Lanchin has been talking to one Cambodian who was a young boy at the time.</p>\n<p>\n\tIt's April, 1975, and the black-uniform soldiers of the Khmer Rouge are making their final push into the Cambodian capital, Phnom Penh. Fear is <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/grip\" target=\"_blank\">gripping</a> the city. Foreign governments are <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/withdraw\" target=\"_blank\">withdrawing</a> their nationals.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;This evacuation is taking place in an effort to ensure the safety of US citizens in Cambodia. We are also undertaking to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/evacuate\" target=\"_blank\">evacuate</a> third-country nationals working for the US government, US press services, voluntary agencies, etc.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\tTens of thousands of Cambodians have already fled the city, among them the mother and sisters of Yuk Chan. The family's ties to the previous government have put them in <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/grave\" target=\"_blank\">grave</a> danger. But 14-year-old Yuk has been left behind to look after the house.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;When the Khmer Rouge came, the whole city, the whole town are silent. I didn't know what's going on. You know, I was a 14-year-old boy. The Khmer Rouge soldiers came to my house and the neighbour and they told us to leave the house, aggressively actually, that we must leave immediately.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: verdana, arial; border-bottom: rgb(0,90,148) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,90,148); line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial; color: rgb(128,128,128); line-height: 25px;\">&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722337/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p722337\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p596036/\">TED演讲：如何在6个月内学会任何一种外语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724208/\">一饱眼福！这10个国家总是产美女！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p628819/\">为什么睡过头反而更疲倦?</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723989/\">太震惊！现实中也有“灰姑娘”</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p704005/\">美元为何叫1刀 货币名称起源大盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724091/\">新东方名师邱政政:四步打造地道美音II</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723668/\">2015两会 李克强答记者问双语全文</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p722342/\">从咀嚼方式看性格 你属于哪一种？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723799/